# Media Company Business Intelligence Project

This project demonstrates the design and implementation of a Business Intelligence system for a media company.

The project includes:

• Data cleaning using Python
• Data warehouse design using PostgreSQL
• Constellation data model
• KPI tracking for 10 departments
• Interactive dashboards built with Power BI

---

## Architecture

Data Sources (Excel files)
        ↓
Data Cleaning (Python / Pandas)
        ↓
PostgreSQL Data Warehouse
        ↓
Constellation Schema
        ↓
Power BI Dashboards

---

## Technologies Used

- Python (Pandas)
- PostgreSQL
- SQL
- Power BI
- GitHub

---

## Dashboards

The BI system includes dashboards for:

- Content Performance
- Audience Engagement
- Subscriptions
- Advertising Revenue
- Editorial Productivity
- Competitive Analysis
- Infrastructure Monitoring
- Governance & Strategy

---

## Project Status

Work in progress – data modeling and ETL development.
